3
00:00:18.095 --> 00:00:19.956
Yeah.

4
00:00:20.056 --> 00:00:22.997
Yeah. easy. Easy.

5
00:00:23.097 --> 00:00:25.318
[low whinny]

6
00:00:25.418 --> 00:00:27.418
Oh.

7
